orizon. From area bound we derive entropy\nbound. These thermodynamic products on the multi horizon playing a crucial role\nin BH thermodynamics to understand the microscopic nature of BH entropy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2013 18:54:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Aug 2014 10:50:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2015 05:43:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-15"}
